.TH "drm_any_plane_has_format" 9 "drm_any_plane_has_format" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
drm_any_plane_has_format \- Check whether any plane supports this format and modifier combination
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" drm_any_plane_has_format
.BI "(struct drm_device *dev "  ","
.BI "u32 format "  ","
.BI "u64 modifier "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
DRM device
.IP "format" 12
pixel format (DRM_FORMAT_*)
.IP "modifier" 12
data layout modifier
.SH "RETURN"
Whether at least one plane supports the specified format and modifier combination.
